<div style="margin:0.5em;">
    <div style="background-color:lightgrey;width:100%;height:6em;display:flex;color:white;">
        <p style="font-weight:bold;font-size:1.5em;text-align:center;margin:auto;">Snow Tricks</p>
    </div>
    <div style="width:70%;margin:auto;color:black;padding:3em;">
        <h2>Hi, {{ user.firstname }}</h2>

        <p>You recently requested to reset your password for your SnowTricks account. Click the button below to reset
            it.</p>

        <a style="width:8rem;display:block;background-color:#007bff;border-color:#007bff;color:white;padding:.375rem.75rem;margin:auto;line-height: 1.5;border-radius:.25rem;text-align:center;"
           href="{{ url('app_reset_password', {token: resetToken.token}) }}">Reset my password</a>

        <p>If you did not request a password reset, just ignore this email or reply to this email to let us know. The
            password
            reset will expire
            in {{ resetToken.expirationMessageKey|trans(resetToken.expirationMessageData, 'ResetPasswordBundle') }}.</p>
        <p>Cheers!</p>
    </div>
    <div style="background-color:lightgrey;width:100%;height:6em;display:flex;color:white;">
        <p style="font-weight:bold;font-size:1.5em;text-align:center;margin:auto;">Snow Tricks</p>
    </div>
</div>